
 ***** tell command *****

syntax: /tell player_name message

where 'player_name' is exact name
of player to which this message
should go,
and where 'message' is the text you 
want player with 'player_name'
to recieve.

IMPORTANT: this commands allows for
private conversations. No other player
than 'player_name' is able to listen
to this message.
